NKOSIKHONA CELE ASATHUKA izanya amalungu omndeni wakwaGina awu-11, endaweni yaseMange eMkhuze, aphunyuke ethunjwe yizigilamkhuba ebezikade zihlasele kuleli khaya ngezithuba zasentathakusa ngesonto eledlule. Ngokuthola kweSolezwe NgoMgqibelo, lezi zigilamkhuba zifike kulo muzi zihlome ziyizingovolo zatshela uMnuz Vusi Gina ukuthi azizile ukuzodlala kodwa zizosebenza. Kuthiwa zingene ngamawindi zashaqa wonke umuntu obesendlini okubalwa nosana olunezinsuku luzelwe. Uthe babalayishe ezimotweni zalo mndeni, bahamba nabo beboshiwe. “Asazi ngempela ukuthi ngobani laba abangaze basicabangele into ebuhlungu kanjena. Namanje sisathukile kakhulu. Ngiyazibuza ukuthi ngempela yini le engaka esiyonile kubani?’’ kubalisa uMnuz Gina. Uthe bonke balaxazwe endlini emnyama emzini abangawazi, bavalelwa izinsuku ezintathu bengadli futhi bengaphuzi lutho. Nosana bathi belukhala lukhalile. Kula malungu omndeni kubalwa unkosikazi wakhe, izingane ezine namanye amalungu. UGina uthi ngenhlanhla bonke bakwazile ukweqa lapho abebethunjwe khona, uthi babuzile ukuthi yikuphi kule ndawo, batshelwa ukuthi baseHlabazini, eManguzi. “Kubantu esibuze kubona basitshele ukuthi siseManguzi. Siyabonga ukuthi sonke sibuye siphephile,’’ kusho uGina. Ubabaza unya lwezigilamkhuba lokungabi nanozwelo lokuthi bathumbe nosana oluncane. UGina uthe inhliziyo yakhe iyabalisa ngemoto yakhe abayebile, waveza ukuthi lezi zigilamkhuba zintshontshe izimoto ezimbili. Eyodwa uthi amaphoyisa ayitholile. Okhulumela amaphoyisa eKwaZulu Natal, uColonel Thembeka Mbele usiqisekisile isigameko. Uthe leli cala lisaphenywa. Uthe kusolakala ukuthi kube nezigilamkhuba ezihlasele umndeni wakwaGina. “Kusolakala ukuthi umndeni waseMange, eMkhuze uhlaselwe ngabantu abebehlomile. Babathumbile beba nezimoto. Enye yezimoto igcine itholakala eManguzi,’’ kusho uCol Mbele. 